Com&Buy Ship For Me & Buy For Me
Provide you with one-stop safe and reliable purchasing, logistics and transportation services!

【 How to use 】
1. Ship For Me - You can click "添加包裹" on the Taobao/Tmall purchased page, and then you can directly submit the delivery information to the Com&Buy website. In addition, you can also edit the added packages.
2. Buy For Me - You can click "我要代购" on the Taobao/Tmall product page to directly add the product to the Com&Buy shopping cart.
3. To browse Com&Buy website - Click the Com&Buy icon on the right side of the browser, and a small window will appear to display the Com&Buy website.

【 Our services 】
Provide simple, reasonable, safe and fast shipping, air, sea, and express services from China to Singapore / Malaysia / International.

【 Website 】
https://comnbuy.com/

Thank you very much for using our Chrome application.
With your support, we will continue to do better.

Com&Buy 代运和代购 
为您提供中国商品一站式安全，可靠的集运、代购、物流运输服务!

【 如何使用 】
1. 代运 - 您可以在淘宝/天猫已买到宝贝的页面点击 “添加包裹”，就可以直接提交代收货信息到Com&Buy网站。此外，您也可以编辑已添加包裹。
2. 代购 - 您可以在淘宝/天猫商品的页面点击 “我要代购”，就可以直接添加商品到Com&Buy购物车。
3. 浏览 Com&Buy 网站 - 点击浏览器右侧的Com&Buy图标，即会出现小窗口显示Com&Buy网站。

【 我们的服务 】
提供简单，合理，安全与快速的海运、空运、海运、快递服务，中国至 马来西亚 / 新加坡 / 国际。

非常感谢使用我们的Chrome应用。
有你们的支持，我们会继续做得更好。
